Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒她...艾拉諾…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒得更厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿冰來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽、普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳們說...剛才我夢到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和媽媽、普莉西絲一起在外面玩得好高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的天空又寬又大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好多漂亮的小花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉諾、艾拉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊!比我想得還要快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子恐怕…恐怕活不了太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能救救她嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用的辦法我都用過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠找到月光花的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲…已經讓村民分成幾路去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不敢保證她不會進入林卡聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能夠盡快找到月光花回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼醫生，您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉諾這邊就要請波曼醫師多費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個只不過是一個古代生物的骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一隻小免子，喂…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免子怎麼變成了怪物了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以被牠打敗呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把月光花找到帶回村子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我製造的東西還是第一次成功的達成任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓，你怎麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我好像聽到普莉西絲的聲音哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我什麼都沒有聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再拖拖拉拉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從現在開始得要用走的嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛~~~ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要突然這麼大聲行不行啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我擔心嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德，你有沒有聽到什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…依我看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲也許還沒有到這裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，是你聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來…是有這個墊著的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爬上去很困難欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有試試這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過了這片森林之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是林卡聖地的中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方應該有長月光花才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們不覺得很奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林卡聖地應該是個充滿危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們到現在都還沒有遇到任何的怪物欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽…有聲音欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了，艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這一次非常確定是個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的聽到普莉西絲的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓!沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是有什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰可以…救救我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我，救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲，我馬上去救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓，危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請掌管『火』之火界王巴拉蒙賜予我祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請汝帶著宛如火箭之身來此降威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火焚牆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個…陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個冒牌貨應該可以露出真面目了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒意思欸，怎麼會被妳識破了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳是普莉西絲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才就應該會直接向克勞德求救才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是找艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的普莉西絲在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳少裝蒜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道她到過這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有多久就被小免子給追跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小免子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，牠是我的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多免子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個體型好像差太多了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠們都是我最寶貝的寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠們一直在這裡等你們來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪我們在路上都沒有碰到什麼妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個人呢，馬上就會變成我的養分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小免子們通通一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天雷電波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭怪物，竟敢用普莉西絲的樣子騙我!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個怎麼會這麼厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這關係到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫做艾拉諾的小女孩的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都要去哪裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就只剩下妳一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還想繼續打嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…我以後不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你們道歉，不要打我 我們沒有要打妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這一次主要是要找一種叫做月光花的草藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一找到我們就會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳得答應我們今後不再攻擊人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不攻擊人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她真的不攻擊人類的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不是非殺她不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我們真的可以相信她嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道月光花開在什麼地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜、塞麗奴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的那些全是胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲，是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光花真的就在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是才說不攻擊人類的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，說得也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我立刻放了她們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，在這之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾…蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓電光明滅的雷界王米塔龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓世人見識你的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天雷電波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是被我親過的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全都會變成供我使喚的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是答應過你們，我自己是不會去攻擊人類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她們就難說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾拉諾比起來，這根本就不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等著，艾拉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就帶月光花回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有找到月光花嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧?艾拉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她頂多只能再撐個半天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到處都找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲好像不在林卡鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她真的是去林卡聖地了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望她不要出事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在能做的也只有祈禱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他們能夠盡快的帶著月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安的回到村子裡面來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快點醒醒啊，蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你孕育光芒一閃的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這些惡徒卑鄙的心思一次迎頭痛擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電波神箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個也不要老是躲來躲去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟她們打一打嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得我都覺得沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳休想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應過要保護蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會傷害她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，那你就等著被她打死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險的應該是塞麗奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離得再遠她也會攻擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想辦法阻擋她的攻擊才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德，我需要你的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時幫我阻擋蕾娜的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼擋啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上格鬥術的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學過一套阻擋對方攻擊的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有試試看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，小圓我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育光芒一閃的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這些惡徒卑鄙的心思一次迎頭痛擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把妳打到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個就會正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以後不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再上妳的當了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是沒有辦法…殺女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像白水晶一樣閃耀的花朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到魔石的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓整個森林都變了樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在她清醒前融化的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓，這是你搞的鬼對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你馬上給我解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了要打倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我得去找月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個妖怪說得對，這裡本來有月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想它們的營養定全被怪物吸掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是......
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易才到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是普莉西絲的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓你怎麼又來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在馬上拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…我好不容易才拿到月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還說好，等她好了要一起出去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事上都會說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子在這個時候及時趕到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是妳…我一直在找妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?有沒有哪裡受傷?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子艾拉諾有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了妳，普莉西絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經渡過危險期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是等她的體力恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，波曼醫生謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也謝謝你，克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我算什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓，好可憐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平就猜到會有這種結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳好了以後我們一起去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，普莉西絲

